To compile the test suite, you need to link against the CUnit and nghttp2 libraries. Assuming you have the nghttp2 library installed, you can compile the test using the following command:

```sh
gcc -o nghttp2_test nghttp2_test.c -L/path/to/nghttp2/lib -lnghttp2 -lcunit
```

Then, run the compiled test:

```sh
./nghttp2_test
```

This will execute all the tests in the suite and output verbose information about each test's result. Make sure to replace `/path/to/nghttp2/lib` with the actual path to the nghttp2 library on your system.

